dan nak pergi menyidainya di balkoni.

511
00:37:31,510 --> 00:37:32,910
Kenapa awak belum tidur lagi?

512
00:37:36,150 --> 00:37:37,990
Kenapa awak simpannya?

513
00:37:39,750 --> 00:37:41,110
Semuanya barang yang tak berguna.

514
00:37:41,550 --> 00:37:42,430
Saya nak menjualnya.

515
00:37:43,070 --> 00:37:45,070
Kan ini barang yang awak paling suka?

516
00:37:46,470 --> 00:37:48,030
Saya sukanya semasa kecil.

517
00:37:48,300 --> 00:37:49,470
Saya dah besar sekarang.

518
00:37:53,580 --> 00:37:54,270
Betul, mak.

519
00:37:55,190 --> 00:37:56,660
Sebelum universiti bermula,

520
00:37:57,230 --> 00:37:58,710
saya perlu balik Shenhai sekali.

521
00:38:10,470 --> 00:38:11,350
Ding Jun Cong.

522
00:38:12,470 --> 00:38:14,670
Awak tak tidur
dan main permainan lagi?

523
00:38:15,230 --> 00:38:16,390
Hari ini hujung minggu.

524
00:38:17,190 --> 00:38:18,590
Apa masalahnya main permainan?

525
00:38:19,100 --> 00:38:20,910
Awak bakal belajar
di sekolah menengah rendah.

526
00:38:21,830 --> 00:38:24,150
Awak mesti fokus dalam pelajaran.

527
00:38:24,590 --> 00:38:26,790
Jika awak tekun seperti kakak awak,

528
00:38:27,150 --> 00:38:28,310
mak takkan menegur awak.

529
00:38:28,390 --> 00:38:30,270
Kakak belajar sehingga dungu.

530
00:38:30,390 --> 00:38:31,150
Jangan merepek.

531
00:38:32,070 --> 00:38:32,740
Xian Xian.

532
00:38:32,990 --> 00:38:35,110
Awak buat ulang kaji
sehingga lewat malam lagi?

533
00:38:38,870 --> 00:38:40,950
Cikgu Wang beritahu ayah
beberapa hari ini

534
00:38:40,950 --> 00:38:42,190
bahawa kemajuan awak besar.

535
00:38:43,070 --> 00:38:43,950
Keputusan awak baik.

536
00:38:44,180 --> 00:38:45,350
Tapi, ayah nak ingatkan awak.

537
00:38:45,670 --> 00:38:46,470
Jangan kepenatan.

538
00:38:46,910 --> 00:38:49,070
Awak mesti berehat juga.
Jangan jejaskan kesihatan.

539
00:38:50,550 --> 00:38:51,310
Saya faham.

540
00:38:55,940 --> 00:38:56,870
Saya balik ke bilik dulu.

541
00:38:58,870 --> 00:39:00,110
Awak tak banyak makan.

542
00:39:00,270 --> 00:39:00,870
Saya dah kenyang.

543
00:39:03,100 --> 00:39:04,510
Dia tak boleh teruskannya.

544
00:39:04,710 --> 00:39:07,110
Dia semakin tak bermaya.

545
00:39:08,030 --> 00:39:09,950
Saya dengar dia bercakap
semasa bermimpi semalam.

546
00:39:10,270 --> 00:39:11,550
Dia menghafal formula semasa bermimpi.

547
00:39:12,830 --> 00:39:13,750
Saya dah hilang akal.

548
00:39:13,830 --> 00:39:15,590
Apa kata awak nasihati dia?

549
00:39:15,990 --> 00:39:16,550
Saya tak nak.

550
00:39:18,110 --> 00:39:19,550
Saya membantah dia belajar semula

551
00:39:19,790 --> 00:39:22,230
sebab risau dia terjerumus dalamnya.

552
00:39:22,710 --> 00:39:24,030
Apa tujuan dia?

553
00:39:24,110 --> 00:39:25,390
Cukup, jangan cakap lagi.

554
00:39:25,390 --> 00:39:26,390
Tak guna awak cakap juga.

555
00:39:27,030 --> 00:39:27,950
Apa nak buat?

556
00:39:29,270 --> 00:39:30,350
Saya tak tahu.

557
00:39:31,380 --> 00:39:32,630
Nasihat seseorang,

558
00:39:33,030 --> 00:39:34,900
kakak mungkin akan dengar.

559
00:39:35,430 --> 00:39:36,150
Siapa?

560
00:39:42,350 --> 00:39:43,350
Mak, saya tak lapar.

561
00:39:43,350 --> 00:39:45,190
Saya tak makan tengah hari.
Mak tak perlu tunggu saya.

562
00:39:45,710 --> 00:39:46,990
Xian Xian, saya ini.

563
00:39:55,430 --> 00:39:56,190
Senior.

564
00:39:56,870 --> 00:39:58,220
Kan awak di Jiangling.

565
00:39:58,790 --> 00:40:00,110
Saya datang jenguk pak cik dan mak cik,

566
00:40:00,150 --> 00:40:01,150
pun jenguk awak juga.

567
00:40:01,990 --> 00:40:03,060
Ayuh. Keluar berjalan-jalan.

568
00:40:04,070 --> 00:40:05,990
Jangan asyik buat ulang kaji dalam bilik.

569
00:40:10,390 --> 00:40:12,430
Ibu bapa saya suruh awak datang?

570
00:40:15,150 --> 00:40:16,470
Mereka risaukan awak.

571
00:40:18,830 --> 00:40:19,780
Saya baik.

572
00:40:22,950 --> 00:40:23,950
Belajar semula

573
00:40:25,630 --> 00:40:26,550
sangat memenatkan?

574
00:40:29,670 --> 00:40:31,870
Ada ramai orang yang lebih penat
daripada saya.

575
00:40:34,430 --> 00:40:36,150
Sedikit kesusahan ini hanya hal remeh.

576
00:40:41,390 --> 00:40:42,070
Senior.

577
00:40:43,390 --> 00:40:44,390
Awak tahu?

578
00:40:47,230 --> 00:40:50,460
Kelas kami ada seorang pelajar
yang bernama Lin You.

579
00:40:51,900 --> 00:40:53,750
Dah tiga tahun dia belajar semula.

580
00:40:54,980 --> 00:40:57,310
Dia nak masuk ke Universiti Nanjing
setiap tahun.

581
00:40:58,350 --> 00:40:59,670
Tapi setiap tahun,

582
00:41:00,390 --> 00:41:02,230
keputusan dia semakin merosot.

583
00:41:03,670 --> 00:41:06,310
Saya rasa dia pelajar yang paling serius
dan paling berusaha

584
00:41:06,390 --> 00:41:07,790
dalam kelas kami.

585
00:41:08,990 --> 00:41:11,230
Tapi, semakin dia berusaha,
semakin mudah dia gagal.

586
00:41:12,110 --> 00:41:13,350
Suatu hari, dalam kelas,

587
00:41:13,580 --> 00:41:14,950
dia hilang kawalan

588
00:41:14,950 --> 00:41:17,270
dan koyakkan semua buku dan kertas soalan.

589
00:41:21,940 --> 00:41:22,700
Belajar semula

590
00:41:25,750 --> 00:41:27,070
betul-betul menakutkan.

591
00:41:29,630 --> 00:41:30,230
Xian Xian.

592
00:41:32,550 --> 00:41:33,910
Awak betul-betul fikir begini?

593
00:41:37,110 --> 00:41:37,870
Sebenarnya,

594
00:41:38,990 --> 00:41:40,270
walaupun awak betul-betul rasa penat,

595
00:41:41,390 --> 00:41:43,230
walaupun awak nak berhenti sekejap
dan berehat sekejap,

596
00:41:45,350 --> 00:41:46,510
tiada orang akan salahkan awak.

597
00:41:52,870 --> 00:41:53,670
Senior.

598
00:41:56,590 --> 00:41:57,670
Saya sangat penat.

599
00:41:58,870 --> 00:42:00,470
Saya betul-betul sangat penat.


